  "local_port": 32916,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the best Android app for listening to and downloading English songs with lyrics?",
  "response": "Choosing the \"best\" Android app for listening to and downloading English songs with lyrics depends on your specific needs, such as user interface preferences, subscription costs, offline capabilities, and the comprehensiveness of lyrics features. However, several standout apps consistently receive high praise for their functionality and user experience. Here are some top recommendations:\n\n### 1. **Spotify**\n\n**Features:**\n- **Extensive Music Library:** Access to millions of English songs across various genres.\n- **Lyrics Integration:** Spotify provides real-time lyrics for many tracks through its \"Behind the Lyrics\" feature, powered by Musixmatch.\n- **Offline Listening:** Available with a Premium subscription, allowing you to download songs for offline use.\n- **Personalized Playlists:** Curated playlists based on your listening habits.\n\n**Pros:**\n- User-friendly interface.\n- Seamless cross-device synchronization.\n- High-quality audio streaming.\n\n**Cons:**\n- Premium features require a subscription.\n- Not all songs have available lyrics.\n\n**Download Link:** [Spotify on Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.spotify.music)\n\n### 2. **Musixmatch**\n\n**Features:**\n- **Comprehensive Lyrics Database:** Access to synchronized lyrics for millions of songs.\n- **Music Player Integration:** Can sync with other music apps like Spotify, Apple Music, and YouTube Music to display lyrics in real-time.\n- **Offline Lyrics:** Available with the Premium subscription.\n\n**Pros:**\n- Excellent for lyric enthusiasts.\n- Supports multiple languages.\n- Customizable lyric display.\n\n**Cons:**\n- Requires integration with another music streaming service to play songs.\n- Some features are behind a paywall.\n\n**Download Link:** [Musixmatch on Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.musixmatch.android.lyrify)\n\n### 3. **Deezer**\n\n**Features:**\n- **Large Music Catalog:** Millions of tracks, including a vast selection of English songs.\n- **Lyrics Feature:** Real-time synchronized lyrics available for many songs.\n- **Offline Mode:** Download songs for offline listening with a Deezer Premium subscription.\n- **Flow Feature:** Personalized soundtrack based on your listening habits.\n\n**Pros:**\n- High-quality audio options (HiFi with lossless FLAC if subscribed).\n- Easy to use interface.\n- Available in multiple languages.\n\n**Cons:**\n- Premium features require a subscription.\n- Lyrics availability may vary.\n\n**Download Link:** [Deezer on Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=deezer.android.app)\n\n### 4. **YouTube Music**\n\n**Features:**\n- **Vast Library:** Access to official songs, covers, live performances, and more.\n- **Lyrics Display:** Some tracks offer synced lyrics through integration with third-party services.\n- **Offline Listening:** Available with YouTube Music Premium.\n- **Personalized Recommendations:** Based on your viewing and listening history.\n\n**Pros:**\n- Comprehensive content including videos.\n- Seamless integration with Google services.\n- User-friendly interface.\n\n**Cons:**\n- Lyrics feature is not as robust as specialized apps like Musixmatch.\n- Premium subscription required for offline downloads.\n\n**Download Link:** [YouTube Music on Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.google.android.apps.youtube.music)\n\n### 5. **Apple Music**\n\n**Features:**\n- **Extensive Music Library:** Millions of English songs.\n- **Lyrics Integration:** Full-screen, synchronized lyrics available for most tracks.\n- **Offline Downloading:** Download songs for offline access with a subscription.\n- **High-Quality Audio:** Supports lossless and spatial audio.\n\n**Pros:**\n- High-quality streaming options.\n- Curated playlists and radio shows.\n- Integration with Apple ecosystem.\n\n**Cons:**\n- Primarily optimized for Apple devices, though available on Android.\n- Subscription-based with no free tier.\n\n**Download Link:** [Apple Music on Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apple.android.music)\n\n### Honorable Mention: **Gaana**\n\n**Features:**\n- **Large Music Library:** Focused on Indian and international English songs.\n- **Lyrics Feature:** In-app lyrics display for many tracks.\n- **Offline Listening:** Available with Gaana Plus subscription.\n- **Personalized Recommendations:** Based on your listening history.\n\n**Pros:**\n- Multiple regional and international content.\n- Affordable subscription plans.\n- User-friendly interface.\n\n**Cons:**\n- Ads in the free version can be intrusive.\n- Lyrics feature may not be as comprehensive as dedicated apps.\n\n**Download Link:** [Gaana on Google Play](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gaana)\n\n### Tips for Choosing the Right App:\n\n1. **Lyrics Availability:** If having access to synchronized lyrics is a top priority, apps like Musixmatch combined with Spotify or Deezer might be the best choice.\n\n2. **Subscription Budget:** Consider whether you're willing to pay for premium features. Many apps offer free tiers with limitations.\n\n3. **Offline Access:** Ensure the app supports downloading songs for offline listening if you need this feature.\n\n4. **Audio Quality:** If high-fidelity audio is important to you, look for apps that offer lossless streaming options.\n\n5. **User Interface:** The ease of use and aesthetic appeal can significantly impact your listening experience. Try a few apps to see which interface you prefer.\n\n### Conclusion\n\nWhile there isn't a one-size-fits-all answer, **Spotify** and **Deezer** are excellent all-around choices offering extensive music libraries, robust lyrics features, and reliable offline capabilities. If lyrics are your primary focus, pairing **Musixmatch** with your preferred music streaming service might provide the best experience. Evaluate the features that matter most to you and consider trying out free tiers before committing to a subscription.",
